[03:24.85]	SONG.
[03:25.62]	Tell me where is fancy bred,
[03:27.98]	Or in the heart, or in the head?
[03:30.54]	How begot, how nourished?
[03:32.62]	Reply, reply.
[03:33.87]	It is engender'd in the eyes,
[03:36.30]	With gazing fed; and fancy dies
[03:38.87]	In the cradle where it lies.
