[03:51.15]	The world is still deceived with ornament.
[03:54.48]	In law, what plea so tainted and corrupt,
[03:57.67]	But, being seasoned with a gracious voice,
[04:00.93]	Obscures the show of evil? In religion,
[04:03.98]	What damned error, but some sober brow
